{"tid":446774,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"博多 -> 別府, 巴士/JR 求助區","createTime":"2017-10-24T15:16:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T05:17:25.000Z","uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1ed9648ebf2055d4025f2a4ddef63bfaedcd4292","tid":446774,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T15:16:03.000Z","msg":"博多去別府果架JR 好似因為打風吹爛左?<br />\n變相要改路, 時間長左好多<br />\n<br />\n所以小妹決定坐巴士去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無巴打絲打知道巴士係唔係要好早訂飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋想問下如果由博多去別府, 有無直接車去海地獄?<br />\n定係點都要先去別府站, 再轉市內巴士去海地獄?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"272e4dfddbdbe74ef495588530b67a530dd2a37d","tid":446774,"uid":19310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T15:27:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://jrkyushu.co.jp/common/inc/emergency/__icsFiles/afieldfile/2017/09/29/170929_1002keikaku.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjrkyushu.co.jp%2Fcommon%2Finc%2Femergency%2F__icsFiles%2Fafieldfile%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F170929_1002keikaku.pdf&d=BE8umleqyV4iKsUKwd3M4wHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=c17e6066\" target=\"_blank\">http://jrkyushu.co.jp/common/inc/emergency/__icsFiles/afieldfile/2017/09/29/170929_1002keikaku.pdf</a><br />\nJR冇問題喎"},{"pid":"9d62de5efd962d329f88ffb72fdfa231dd406692","tid":446774,"uid":34692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T15:52:08.000Z","msg":"係去由布院先有問題<br />\n別府坐JR一切正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa408869a93b63186e623d8a88bb45faa6f429a","tid":446774,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T16:30:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係去由布院先有問題<br />\n別府坐JR一切正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係要4粒鐘咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04030827d01d382a45eec2d7ec73690316442552","tid":446774,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T16:43:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係去由布院先有問題<br />\n別府坐JR一切正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係要4粒鐘咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來2粒鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.jrkyushu.co.jp/english/pdf/timetable_20170304_20180228.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jrkyushu.co.jp%2Fenglish%2Fpdf%2Ftimetable_20170304_20180228.pdf&d=BE8umleqyV4iKsUKwd3M4wHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=6660c074\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.jrkyushu.co.jp/english/pdf/timetable_20170304_20180228.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n咁另外想問下，別府去由布院係唔係一定要巴士？<br />\n因為我買左由布院既溫泉酒店，果時好似7點幾要返到去食個dinner"},{"pid":"e88b2afb6f9555323b580950e6584bca354a8ea9","tid":446774,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T17:18:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.jrkyushu.co.jp/railway/routemap/routemap.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jrkyushu.co.jp%2Frailway%2Froutemap%2Froutemap.pdf&d=BE8umleqyV4iKsUKwd3M4wHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=4f31ca42\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.jrkyushu.co.jp/railway/routemap/routemap.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n●日田彦山線（上下線）<br />\n　【運転見合わせ：添田　から　夜明】<br />\n●久大本線（上下線）<br />\n　【運転見合わせ：光岡　から　日田】<br />\n<br />\n吹爛左既部分都唔係你去既地方　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7bebe76c04e2b2eecf274b1b7fd9f803f42fb8d","tid":446774,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T02:48:47.000Z","msg":"想問埋熊本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係好明佢個price<br />\n如果就咁買自由席, 係唔係2130yen?<br />\n<br />\nor一定要買特急劵?<br />\n<br />\n點解又有分指定同自由席? (同價錢?)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/02/104603_9d37d2dec83919d3fa3fb136eaa9d58a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F02%2F104603_9d37d2dec83919d3fa3fb136eaa9d58a.jpg&h=a9d84853&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c133c918d6b67c13a4dff00e7955dcfeeb3ebf4","tid":446774,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T02:53:19.000Z","msg":"呢度就寫2130 乘車 + 2800 指定席<br />\n<br />\n咁如果我就咁坐自由席的話, 係唔係2130 就ok?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/02/105301_31122a70476dc9792f8c6098ad9c7617.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F02%2F105301_31122a70476dc9792f8c6098ad9c7617.jpg&h=313be449&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"660c0af9aca52aff25d172bf3e2220dc95f3935c","tid":446774,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:01:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢度就寫2130 乘車 + 2800 指定席<br />\n<br />\n咁如果我就咁坐自由席的話, 係唔係2130 就ok?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/02/105301_31122a70476dc9792f8c6098ad9c7617.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F02%2F105301_31122a70476dc9792f8c6098ad9c7617.jpg&h=313be449&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乘車券 2130 只係包你坐普通或者快速(即係你見到要兩個鐘先到嗰D車)<br />\n要坐新幹線一定要買新幹線特急券<br />\n自由席會平少少，無畫位，有位就坐無位就要企<br />\n指定席就一定有位"},{"pid":"01c26aa0bb641afe758b93478d59ee98cd2ecaeb","tid":446774,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:17:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢度就寫2130 乘車 + 2800 指定席<br />\n<br />\n咁如果我就咁坐自由席的話, 係唔係2130 就ok?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/02/105301_31122a70476dc9792f8c6098ad9c7617.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F02%2F105301_31122a70476dc9792f8c6098ad9c7617.jpg&h=313be449&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乘車券 2130 只係包你坐普通或者快速(即係你見到要兩個鐘先到嗰D車)<br />\n要坐新幹線一定要買新幹線特急券<br />\n自由席會平少少，無畫位，有位就坐無位就要企<br />\n指定席就一定有位</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家睇緊巴士<br />\n<br />\n博多站3F -&gt; 熊本交通巴士站<br />\n2個幾鐘, 仲可以用SunQ pass<br />\n<br />\n一落車行過去就係熊本城, 唔洗再另外坐車<br />\n<br />\n唔知有無睇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}